司使用 AI 聊天机器人与候选人交流。大约 23% 的公司使用 AI 进行面试，64% 的公司使用 AI 来审查候选人评估。多家国内银行采用 AI 面试进行招聘，以提高效率"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-97ab05042a7552b43dc6c561b026af5c_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "35 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/6469875278"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI/MGW3/z0vrxHEAMaCTExMjI3MDUyOCDptt+6BjAAOGlAFXIKNjQ2OTg3NTI3OHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1734088766.95035", "card_id": "Q_596850652", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 111}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如果描述一个武将有万夫不当之勇，你认为他能打几个？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-610e93c12f18766c7c9d462569cf3b84_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "20 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/596850652"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I/MGW3/z0vrxHEAMaCDk0OTE0MjIxILmhhqIGMAA49wFAFnIJNTk2ODUwNjUyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "23_1734088766.95383", "card_id": "Q_6471102812", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 33}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "日语中使用「你（あなた /anata） 」据说过于暧昧，为什么日本影视作品动漫中却使用得很多？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "见过不少日本人谈这个词，都说会尽量避免使用 那么为何在作品里用得那么多？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-3d5c1d6be3c9f36491a4db02b9a3df71_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "18 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/6471102812"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI/MGW3/z0vrxHEAMaCTExMjI3MDc3NiClvt+6BjAAOGtAF3IKNjQ3MTEwMjgxMngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "ho